         <abstract>
            <p>This hymn is ascribed to John Chrysostom. The hymn itself begins with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተፈሥሒ፡ ኦእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>, which is repeated after each stanza.
            In most manuscripts it is preceded by a preamble varying in structure and length, which begins with <foreign xml:lang="gez">እሰግድ፡ ለኪ፡ ወእዌድሰኪ፡ ኦእግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡</foreign>.</p>
         </abstract>
